snippet.title: Terra Ventura Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Terra Ventura is an action adventure game set in fantasy world with RPG elements. Release date is set for Q4 2021. You can see the store page at https://store.steampowered.com/app/1664580?utm_campaign=youtube or learn more at https://logicalprogression.tech
